Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:40.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:12.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:15.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:26.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:30.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:33.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:45.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:40.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:12.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:15.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:26.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:30.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:33.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:45.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}心灵之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:43.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:49.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:58.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:06.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:15.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:23.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:31.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:39.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:47.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:55.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:43.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:49.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:58.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:06.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:15.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:23.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:31.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:39.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:47.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:55.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不躲开的话就要被踩扁了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个烦人的苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤到城寨里面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为这样的东西能抵挡得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是我的主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖励一下你们的顽强斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们全杀掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的应该是白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该在这里浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤亡越大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就越是不会眼睁睁的看着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 百姓的避难还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和胧一起去圣上那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭的 就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝纳威 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上 为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们由我来牵制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止大家十分努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好了能够封锁阿弗·卡姆的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有时间来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在下也一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让圣上一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵从圣上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库涅卡门的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止无意义的杀戮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 如我所说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于现身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料你也只是害怕得嗦嗦发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁滚尿流地一直躲着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 人害怕得嗦嗦发抖时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是会屁滚尿流的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭着跪下来向我求饶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话放过你也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哭着跪下来请求饶命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能得救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我可不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 你可真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来陪你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有说要我活着带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微弄坏一点也不要紧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愚蠢了 竟受激将法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使违抗圣上的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也不会让你通过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 牵制的任务是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 对策根本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看到阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不是和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到的时候已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆库鲁也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是副好样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维恩库亚大人 应该停手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我不会杀他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微弄坏他一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许欺负爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维恩库亚大人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是我的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是弄伤了我美丽的阿弗·卡姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使哭也不会原谅你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 绝不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要保护爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠似的到处乱转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得意了 你这低等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露…露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想听这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对玩厌的玩具只剩下弄坏它了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗…阿露露…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了 终于解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维恩库亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 刚才那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修科 尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 阿露露 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…恐龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 这个是和人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用两条腿走路的生物的骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这雕像实在太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋的人 我不是叮嘱过不要涉足这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把这个隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能承认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿猴进化成人类过程中的空白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Missing Link
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48}注：Missing Link，推测在人类和猴之间的过渡生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个答案要是就在你的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进化的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有它 人类或许将永远是猿猴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个怪物吗 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学者真是处世艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被多余的好奇心驱使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖出不该挖出的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 招致杀身之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 救我 妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起死…回生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和她说过不要一个人跑到森林深处的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么厉害的地震 我还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 来人啊 来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止不住 血止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来帮帮我 谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小女孩的生命 想救活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渺小之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 拜托了 救救阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论要我怎么回报都可以 所以 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 将汝之一切献给吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将汝之身体 从每一根发丝到每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将汝那无垢之灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将汝的一切献给吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝说的愿意做一切只是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给你 我的身心 一切都献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 契约成立
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现汝之愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了阿露露 献出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个…到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗 你要喝点茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 这里… 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库涅卡门怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经撤退了 大家都回来了 请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露呢 阿露露怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露的话 在院子里玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好休息 哈克奥罗很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是我吗


